trans-unit.source: black developers for an awesome formatting tool
trans-unit.target: 黑人开发人员提供了很棒的格式化工具

trans-unit.source: mypy for doing all dirty work for us
trans-unit.target: mypy为我们做了所有肮脏的工作
Client 每个服务的客户端类型注释
Paginator 每个服务的分页器类型注释

trans-unit.source: PyCharm also supports function overloads, but consumes a lot of RAM, use carefully if you have many services installed
trans-unit.target: PyCharm 还支持函数重载，但会消耗大量RAM，如果已安装许多服务，请谨慎使用
Resource 每个服务的资源类型注释

trans-unit.source: VSCode does not currently support function overloads, use explicit type annotations
trans-unit.target: VSCode 当前不支持函数重载，请使用显式类型注释
Waiter 每个服务的服务员类型注释

trans-unit.source: boto3-stubs uses format <boto3_version>.<build>, e.g. for boto3 1.10.40, boto3-stubs versions are is 1.10.40.0 and 1.10.40.1.
trans-unit.target: boto3-stubs 使用格式 <boto3_version>.<build> ，例如对于 boto3 1.10.40 ， boto3-stubs 版本是 1.10.40.0 和 1.10.40.1 。
boto3-stubs[greengrass] -类型的注释格林格拉斯服务。

trans-unit.source: mypy_boto3 command generates boto3.client/resource type annotations for all installed services.
trans-unit.target: mypy_boto3 命令为所有已安装的服务生成 boto3.client/resource 类型注释。
激活 mypy 签入设置： "python.linting.mypyEnabled": true
所有可用的 boto3 服务均已涵盖。

trans-unit.source: Auto discovery of types for ServiceResource and Resource collections
trans-unit.target: 自动发现 ServiceResource 和 Resource 集合的类型

trans-unit.source: Auto discovery of types for boto3.client and boto3.session calls
trans-unit.target: 自动发现 boto3.client 和 boto3.session 调用的类型

trans-unit.source: Auto discovery of types for client.get_waiter and client.get_paginator calls
trans-unit.target: 自动发现 client.get_waiter 和 client.get_paginator 调用的类型

trans-unit.source: Auto discovery of types for session.client and session.session calls
trans-unit.target: 自动发现 session.client 和 session.session 调用的类型

trans-unit.source: Automatic type discovery is too stressful for PyCharm and does not work in VSCode. So implicit type annotations support has been removed as it is not useful.
trans-unit.target: 自动类型发现对 PyCharm 来说压力太大,而且在 VSCode 中也无法使用。因此,隐式类型注释的支持已经被删除,因为它没有用处。

trans-unit.source: Builder changelog can be found in Releases.
trans-unit.target: 可以在Releases中找到Builder的变更日志。

trans-unit.source: Code is processed by black for readability.
trans-unit.target: 代码以黑色处理以提高可读性。

trans-unit.source: Each public class and method of every boto3 service gets valid type annotations extracted from the documentation (blame botocore docs if types are incorrect).
trans-unit.target: 每个 boto3 服务的每个公共类和方法都将从文档中提取有效的类型注释（如果类型不正确，则指责 botocore 文档）。

trans-unit.source: Fully automated mypy-boto3-builder carefully generates type annotations for each service, patiently waiting for boto3 updates. It delivers a drop-in type annotations for you and makes sure that:
trans-unit.target: 全自动mypy-boto3-builder会仔细地为每个服务生成类型注释，耐心等待 boto3 更新。它为您提供了一个插入式注释，并确保：
全类型带注释的 boto3 库

trans-unit.source: Generated type annotations provide overloads for boto3.client and boto3.resource, boto3.Session.client and boto3.Session.resource functions, so explicit type annotations are not needed.
trans-unit.target: 生成的类型注释为 boto3.client 和 boto3.resource ， boto3.Session.client 和 boto3.Session.resource 函数提供了重载，因此不需要显式的类型注释。

trans-unit.source: Guys behind boto3-type-annotations, this package is based on top of their work
trans-unit.target: boto3-type-annotations背后的家伙，此软件包基于他们的工作成果

trans-unit.source: Install mypy and optionally enable it in your IDE
trans-unit.target: 安装mypy并可以选择在IDE中启用它
安装 boto3-stubs 与 boto3 您使用服务

trans-unit.source: Install boto3-stubs, to add type annotations for boto3 package.
trans-unit.target: 安装 boto3-stubs ，为 boto3 包添加类型注释。

trans-unit.source: It is totally safe to use TYPE_CHECKING flag in order to avoid boto3-stubs dependency in production. However, there is an issue in pylint that it complains about undefined variables. To fix it, set all types to object in non-TYPE_CHECKING mode.
trans-unit.target: 使用 TYPE_CHECKING 标志是完全安全的，以避免 生产中对 boto3-stubs 依赖性。但是， pylint 中存在一个问题，即抱怨未定义的变量。要解决此问题，请在非 TYPE_CHECKING 模式下将所有类型设置为 object 。

trans-unit.source: Link to documentation is provided for every method.
trans-unit.target: 每种方法都提供了文档链接。

trans-unit.source: Make sure you have mypy installed and activated in your IDE.
trans-unit.target: 确保已在IDE中安装并激活了mypy。

trans-unit.source: Official mypy plugin does not work for some reason for me. If you know how to setup it correctly, please hep me to update this section.
trans-unit.target: 由于某些原因，官方的 mypy 插件无法正常工作。如果您知道如何正确设置，请帮助我更新此部分。

trans-unit.source: Set path to mypy in mypy plugin settings
trans-unit.target: 设置路径 mypy 在 mypy plugin 设置

trans-unit.source: To get full advantage of boto3-stubs, you can set types explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 要充分利用 boto3-stubs ，可以显式设置类型。

trans-unit.source: Type annotations for boto3 1.14.50 compatible with mypy, VSCode, PyCharm and other tools.
trans-unit.target: 与mypy，VSCode， PyCharm和其他工具兼容的boto3 1.14.50的类型注释 。

trans-unit.source: Type annotations for boto3 1.14.50, generated by mypy-boto3-buider 2.2.0

trans-unit.target: 类型注释包括最新的文档。

trans-unit.source: Use explicit type annotations because function overload is not fully supported in Python extension.
trans-unit.target: 使用显式类型注解，因为函数重载不完全支持 在 Python 的扩展。

trans-unit.source: Use explicit type annotations for session.client and session.resource calls
trans-unit.target: 对 session.client 和 session.resource 调用使用显式类型注释

trans-unit.source: Use boto3 with mypy_boto3 in your project and enjoy type checking.
trans-unit.target: 在项目 boto3 与 mypy_boto3 一起使用，并享受类型检查。

trans-unit.source: VSCode: Use explicit types for boto3.client, boto3.session.client, client.get_waiter and client.get_paginator calls to enjoy code auto-complete and correct type hints
trans-unit.target: VSCode：为 boto3.client ， boto3.session.client ， client.get_waiter 和 client.get_paginator 调用使用显式类型，以享受代码自动完成和正确的类型提示的作用

trans-unit.source: You need explicit type annotations for code auto-complete, but mypy works even without them.
trans-unit.target: 您需要显式的类型注释来自动完成代码，但是即使没有它们， mypy 也可以工作。
